---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ProfileHeader from '../../components/ProfileHeader.astro';
import CaseStudyCard from '../../components/CaseStudyCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="Student Portal Case Study - Jake Christon">
    <main>
        <ProfileHeader 
            name="Jake Christon"
            title="UI/UX Designer & BSIT Student"
        />

        <section class="case-study">
            <h2>Student Portal Redesign Project</h2>
            
            <div class="project-overview">
                <h3>Project Overview</h3>
                <p>As a BSIT student, I identified the need to improve the student portal experience across both mobile and web platforms. This case study documents my approach to creating a seamless, user-friendly interface for students.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="platforms">
                <div class="platform">
                    <h3>Mobile App Design</h3>
                    <CaseStudyCard
                        title="Mobile Student Portal"
                        description="A native mobile experience designed for quick access to essential student information and services."
                        image="/mobile-portal.png"
                        tags={['Mobile First', 'Native App', 'iOS & Android']}
                    />
                    <div class="key-features">
                        <h4>Key Features:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Biometric login for secure access</li>
                            <li>Push notifications for announcements</li>
                            <li>Offline access to class schedules</li>
                            <li>Mobile-optimized grade viewing</li>
                            <li>Quick enrollment process</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="platform">
                    <h3>Web Application</h3>
                    <CaseStudyCard
                        title="Web Student Portal"
                        description="A comprehensive web platform providing full access to academic services and information."
                        image="/web-portal.png"
                        tags={['Responsive', 'Web App', 'Dashboard']}
                    />
                    <div class="key-features">
                        <h4>Key Features:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Interactive dashboard</li>
                            <li>Advanced course management</li>
                            <li>Document submission system</li>
                            <li>Academic progress tracking</li>
                            <li>Integration with learning platforms</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="design-process">
                <h3>Design Process</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Research Phase</strong>
                        <p>Conducted surveys with 200+ students to understand pain points with existing portal</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>User Flow Mapping</strong>
                        <p>Created detailed user flows for common tasks across both platforms</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Wireframing</strong>
                        <p>Developed low and high-fidelity wireframes using Figma</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Prototyping</strong>
                        <p>Built interactive prototypes for user testing</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Testing & Iteration</strong>
                        <p>Conducted usability testing with 50 students and implemented feedback</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        width: 1000px;
        max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
        color: white;
    }
    .case-study {
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .project-overview {
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .platforms {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .platform {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
    }
    .key-features {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .key-features ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .key-features li {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }
    .key-features li:before {
        content: "â†’";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    }
    .design-process ol {
        list-style-type: none;
        counter-reset: steps;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .design-process li {
        counter-increment: steps;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        padding-left: 3rem;
        position: relative;
    }
    .design-process li:before {
        content: counter(steps);
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>